Description.LocalizedString: Clad head to toe in all-black leather, he cuts an intimidating silhouette.
Clad head to toe in all-black, bloody leather, he cuts a terrifying silhouette.
A brilliant and driven scientist intent on taking humanity to the next level.
A bloody and driven scientist hellbent on taking humanity to the next level.
A bloodied blade with a serrated edge that has torn up his opponents.
A vicious blade with a serrated edge to aid in tearing up his opponents.
A mysterious spy whose true alliance can never really be known.
A mysterious, gore-soaked spy, whose true alliance can never really be known.
Fancy enough to blend in during a high-class event, practical enough to blend in anywhere else.
Fancy enough to blend in during a high-class event, if not for the blood.
An atypical choice for one who moves through the shadows, she prefers it for its mobility.
An atypical choice for one who moves through the shadows, covered in blood.
A brilliant former child prodigy, this rookie member of S.T.A.R.S. is now a talented field medic.
A resilient former child prodigy, this blood-soaked member of S.T.A.R.S. is now a talented field medic.
Complete with all the equipment required to be a valuable field surgeon.
Spattered with blood and complete with all of the equipment required to be a valuable field surgeon.
As the medic, she was the lifeline of the team.
She was often covered in blood. Most of the time, it wasnt hers.
